\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\af5\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af5\langfe255\hich\f4\fs28\lang1033\loch\f4\fs28\lang1033 
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\af5\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af5\langfe255\hich\f4\fs28\lang1033\loch\f4\fs28\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs28\lang1033\i0\b0 At the Tribunal hearing, the Appellants objected to the amendment submitting that there was no proper basis for  the amendment to be allowed.  The  amendment would have caused substantial prejudice to the Appellants.  The Tribunal considered the submission
