al Government and Land Tenure and Another v Sizwe Development and Others: In Re Sizwe Development v Flagstaff Municipality 1991 (1) SA 677 (TK) at 678 \'96 679 and Vandenhende v Minister of Agriculture, Planning and Tourism, Western Cape and Others 2000 (4) S
