\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\af5\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af5\langfe255\hich\f4\fs28\lang1033\loch\f4\fs28\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs28\lang1033\i0\b0 The language of the statute is clear.  There is no reference to interest at all.  The mere requirement is that a party must be recognized by the Tribunal as a participant.  The recognition could be on the basis of some other grounds, other than an interest
